node.text:
Visit @SculptMovements 💕 for workouts, routine, and everythin else you eed to become fit! .
Treino de MMI com 01. Agachamento máquina 15/12/10 + drop com extensora 4 x 4 / 4x3 / 4x2 /4x 1 aumentando a carga ( 1 série ) 
1 x 10 com pico de contração em cima + 10 saindo da inércia 
1 x 10 com excêntrica lenta + 10 concêntrica lenta + 10 
02. Stiff 3 x 15 + bom dia 10 
03. Flexora 9 x 6 alternando a carga entre leva e pesado 
1 x 30 curtas + 10 isometria + 12 
1 x unilateral 8 /7/6 até zerar sem intervalo 
04. Flexora em pé 3 x 12 parando no meio + glúteo no cabo 3 x 12 
Panturrilhas sempre 😅
Macacão @santtaloren
.
.
.
Credit @graoficial #Fitness #fitfam #fitspo #motivation #workout #workoutvideo #legday #gym #abs

node.text:
She looks perfect 😍
cc: @_liline.anne

💣 Shoulder workout (deltas) 🔥 triceps versus jelly branches 😅 Save & @SculptMobility for daily pain management, flexibility, and workout advice📚 
 ⠀
 SAVE 🔰LIKE ♥ ️ - of course I'm waiting for them 😅 this is my motivation from you to continue to share usefulness and even more for free 💯🥰
 ⠀
 Sure❗️😉 you will appreciate the complex as well as me💣😍👻

 ⠀
 3 sets of 12-15 reps👌🏾
 As you can see, I work with low to medium weights.  This is quite enough for the development of deltas.
 ⠀
 Favorite heading 🤩How many exercises for the back delta ❓From me ♥ ️
 ⠀
 📍How will you try to repeat the complex, write your impressions 🤗 it will be very pleasant and interesting for me 😘

Credit • @aina_var #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sculpt Lifestyle on September 19, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'You do not have to lose that big day weight for'.

node.text:
You do not HAVE to LOSE WEIGHT for your big day. Not for your wedding. Not for your graduation. Not for your birthday or your baby’s birthday or any gosh darn birthday.

Even if society tells us otherwise. 

I’ve started getting diet adverts related to weddings.
‘Bridal detoxes’ and ‘get slim fast!’ programs. 

I know why they’re targeting me; 
So many brides DIET before they say ‘I do’. 

But I’m not going to play that game. 
I don’t want to waste a moment of this special time,
Counting calories or struggling to shrink.

For me, ‘TINIER’ and ‘HEALTHIER’ don’t necessarily go hand in hand,
And while I DO have goals,
I’m tying them more to a FEELING than some society-enforced physique. 

So today, I just want to remind you: 

Us women do not HAVE to become LESS,
In order to deserve MORE.

We do not have to make ourselves SMALLER
To live the big, delicious, colorful lives we deserve. 

And we do not have to SHRINK,
In order to CELEBRATE. 
 
So you, you lovely soul,
Drown out the shouts of a 70 billion dollar diet industry, 
And own the magic of your BIG DAY. 

Lean into what feels right to you, FOR YOU. 

And remember that you, exactly as you are RIGHT NOW,
Are worthy of those gorgeous celebrations. 

No dodgy detoxes required. 

x

Credit @danaemercer #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout.

3 pulldown variations for ya ⚡️

Credit @etkfit #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout.

TWIST UP CORE WITH THESE MOVES!

Instead of adding abs at the end of my workout,  I will add them to my warmup and  separated within my hour of lifting which allows for more recovery. 

Go till you can’t. Weights help speed up the time it takes for me to go until failure.

3-4x 
Reps no more than 20 or you need to add more weight.  Must keep abs tightly engaged the entire time. 

SUPERSET
1️⃣Decline Bend to Arm Extension
2️⃣Twists 

3️⃣Hanging Sand Bag Leg Raise 
4️⃣Twists then Dropset Twists 

5️⃣Leg Raise Side Twists

WARMUP
6️⃣Ball & 9lb Bar Twists & Raises
•
•

node.text:
HOLIDAY WORKOUT👙🔥 

Ladies you NEED to check out @SculptSwim for summers hottest bikinis 👙 

Beach walk followed by this body weight burnout!

I always say, don’t underestimate what you can do with just your body🥵

1. 30sec Lunges
2. 30sec Explosive Lunges
3. 30sec Step Ups
4. 30sec Explosive Step Ups
2 Rounds (each leg)

1. 20sec Box Jumps
2. 20sec Side Plank Pulses E/S 
3. 20sec Rotated Plank E/S
3 Rounds 

Let me know if you try this, much harder then it looks🔥

Credit @racheljdillon #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout
